@access_token = SEU_TOKEN_AQUI

### 1. Obter token JWT
POST http://localhost:8000/token
Content-Type: application/x-www-form-urlencoded

username=admin&password=admin123

###

### 2. Chamar /crew
POST http://localhost:8000/crew
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "topic": "Teste de execução"
}

###

### 3. Ver métricas
GET http://localhost:8000/metrics
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}

###

### 4. Simular alerta no /alert-webhook
POST http://localhost:8000/alert-webhook
Authorization: Bearer {{access_token}}
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "status": "firing",
  "labels": {
    "alertname": "HighResponseTimeRogerio",
    "severity": "warning",
    "owner": "Rogerio"
  },
  "annotations": {
    "summary": "Tempo de resposta alto (Rogerio)",
    "description": "Run do CrewAI (owner=Rogerio) acima de 6 segundos."
  }
}
